Shulker boxes in need of an upgrade? No need to gather all new shells, there are 9 upgrade items availible. They will preserve the inventory of your shulker so there is no need to empty it beforehand. 

§n§A§r§lAvailible Upgrades:§l§r
Vanilla -) Copper
Vanilla -) Iron
Copper -) Iron
Copper -) Silver
Iron -) Gold
Silver -) Gold
Gold -) Diamond
Diamond -) Crystal
Diamond -) Obsidian

[note]Hint: You can also use these upgrades to avoid the 50 vis wand requirement of the higher tier shulkers.[/note]
